### Cart Controller Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@accessToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI4MzM3YmM0YS0wZDJmLTRiNzgtYTBkNC0zOTNkZjAwOWJlOTMiLCJlbWFpbCI6InVzZXIxQGV4YW1wbGUuY29tIiwicm9sZSI6IkFETUlOIiwiaWF0IjoxNzgwNjc2OTk2LCJleHAiOjE3ODA2Nzc4OTZ9.ysbo945BeGrFkOOVF9chPUekRQ-wJfQj5fBfE5D2rAg

@variantId = PUT_A_VALID_VARIANT_ID_HERE


### ─── السلة ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get Cart (جلب السلة — تنشئ تلقائياً لو مش موجودة)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: ar


### Add Item to Cart (إضافة عنصر)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variantId": "{{variantId}}",
  "quantity": 2
}


### Add Same Variant Again (تزيد الكمية)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variantId": "{{variantId}}",
  "quantity": 1
}


### Exceed Max Quantity (تجاوز 10)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variantId": "{{variantId}}",
  "quantity": 11
}


### Update Item Quantity (تعديل الكمية)
@itemId = PUT_CART_ITEM_ID_HERE
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/cart/items/{{itemId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: ar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 3
}


### Remove Item (حذف عنصر)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart/items/{{itemId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: ar


### Clear Cart (تفريغ السلة)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: ar


### ─── أخطاء ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Invalid Variant ID (معرف غير صحيح)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: en
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variantId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "quantity": 1
}


### Missing Token (بدون توكن)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart
Accept-Language: ar


### Invalid Quantity (كمية غير صحيحة)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept-Language: en
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variantId": "{{variantId}}",
  "quantity": 0
}
